            "title": "港股開市︱初段跟跌 恒指跌 點報 點 滙控低開0.86%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股開市初段跟隨外圍向下，恒生指數開市報25708點，跌184點或0.71%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數開報4826點，跌33點或0.69%；國企指數以8606點開市，跌48點或0.56%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股普遍下跌，滙控(00005)開報138.5元，跌0.86%；友邦(01299)開報87.1元，跌2.08%。阿里巴巴(09988)開報124.5元，跌0.8%；騰訊(00700)開報498.4元，跌1.21%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15865096-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e8%b7%9f%e8%b7%8c-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c-%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b1-%e9%bb%9e-%e6%bb%99%e6%8e%a7%e4%bd%8e%e9%96%8b0-86",
